skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Developer Terms of Use
des: Anytime you need some advice on learning and living like a warrior, just ask Alexa for your SEAL Training Flash Briefing. You'll get to hear the thoughts and advice from retired Navy SEAL sniper Chris Sajnog. Start your day off right with lessons on training, diet, exercise, motivation and the occasional random drop of dry humor. Appropriate for all ages. Not appropriate for closed minded. Not needed for those who already know it all.
